{"an8.56:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.56 ","an8.56:0.2":"6. Gotamivagga ","an8.56:0.3":"Bhayasutta ","an8.56:1.1":"“‘Bhayan’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.2":"‘Dukkhan’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.3":"‘Rogo’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.4":"‘Gando’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.5":"‘Sallan’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.6":"‘Sango’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.7":"‘Panko’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.8":"‘Gabbho’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.9":"Kasma ca, bhikkhave, ‘bhayan’ti kamanametam adhivacanam? ","an8.56:1.10":"Yasma ca kamaragarattayam, bhikkhave, chandaragavinibaddho ditthadhammikapi bhaya na parimuccati, samparayikapi bhaya na parimuccati, tasma ‘bhayan’ti kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:1.11":"Kasma ca, bhikkhave, ‘dukkhan’ti …pe… ","an8.56:1.12":"‘rogo’ti … ","an8.56:1.13":"‘gando’ti … ","an8.56:1.14":"‘sallan’ti … ","an8.56:1.15":"‘sango’ti … ","an8.56:1.16":"‘panko’ti … ","an8.56:1.17":"‘gabbho’ti kamanametam adhivacanam? ","an8.56:1.18":"Yasma ca kamaragarattayam, bhikkhave, chandaragavinibaddho ditthadhammikapi gabbha na parimuccati, samparayikapi gabbha na parimuccati, tasma ‘gabbho’ti kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an8.56:2.1":"Bhayam dukkhanca rogo ca, ","an8.56:2.2":"gando sallanca sango ca; ","an8.56:2.3":"Panko gabbho ca ubhayam, ","an8.56:2.4":"ete kama pavuccanti; ","an8.56:2.5":"Yattha satto puthujjano. ","an8.56:3.1":"Otinno satarupena, ","an8.56:3.2":"puna gabbhaya gacchati; ","an8.56:3.3":"Yato ca bhikkhu atapi, ","an8.56:3.4":"sampajannam na riccati. ","an8.56:4.1":"So imam palipatham duggam, ","an8.56:4.2":"atikkamma tathavidho; ","an8.56:4.3":"Pajam jatijarupetam, ","an8.56:4.4":"phandamanam avekkhati”ti. ","an8.56:4.5":"Chattham. "}